title: RGP-5: Use of ETH & RBN from Divergence Ventures
body:
This is a vote on how to best use the ETH and RBN returned by Divergence.

Please see the [governance post](https://gov.ribbon.finance/t/rgp-5-use-of-eth-rbn-from-divergence-ventures/264) here for more details.

Note: This vote includes the RBN voting power from staked and unstaked Uniswap V3 LPs in the RBN/ETH 1% pool.
author: 0xa75c86521514Ff4873E5524a2579B249403c9a21
